Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.28,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.61,0:00:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.05,0:00:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗噗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡修陛下好慢哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.63,0:00:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，陛下應該是個用劍高手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.36,0:00:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘恩在三年前都被打到詞窮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙好燙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.81,0:00:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始囉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.01,0:00:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這是這是這是…\N- 啊啊啊啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.80,0:00:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著的騎士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好騎士!(晚安)\N(good knight=>good night)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.46,0:00:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盾牌累了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.92,0:00:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，西魯德!(啊，辛勞了!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.56,0:01:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 龍的運動?\N- 多、多、多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多拉格林?\N(trampoline，彈簧墊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.73,0:01:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准用疑問句回答!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.09,0:01:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼特訓啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.46,0:01:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了!我知道了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.66,0:01:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了，潘恩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.16,0:01:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會陛下進來的第一句話\N一定是穿著甲冑說:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡修(甲冑)\N怎樣?帥氣(甲冑)吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這個沒錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.55,0:01:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈，潘恩真會說笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.01,0:01:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈，再怎麼說也是一國之君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.68,0:01:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會用這麼好笑的方式出場嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.58,0:01:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成長了，潘恩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.45,0:01:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我感到欣喜萬分哪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
